<h1>Cobot Slack Integration</h1>

<p>This software will connect your coworking space on Cobot with your <a href="http://slack.com">Slack.com</a> chat account.</p>

<p>After this, new members on Cobot will automatically be added to your Slack team, so you don't have to add them manually.</p>

<p>Select the space you want to add to Slack:</p>

<table class="table">
  <tbody>
    <% @spaces.each do |space| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= link_to space.name, [:new, space, :team] %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Manage existing teams', space, class: 'pull-right btn btn-mini btn-primary' %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
